(2^b - 1)(1 + 2^b + 2^{2b} + ... + 2^{(a - 1)b}
=2^b(1 + 2^b + 2^{2b} + ... + 2^{(a - 1)b}) - (1 + 2^b + 2^{2b} + ... + 2^{a - 1)b})
=(2^b + 2^{2b} + 2^{3b} + ... + 2^{ab}) - (1 + 2^b + 2^{2b} + ... + 2^{(a - 1)b})
=2^{ab} - 1
