\left(2^b - 1\right)\left(1 + 2^b + 2^{2b} + ... + 2^{(a - 1)b}\right)=\left(2^b - 1\right)\sum_{k=0}^{a-1}2^{bk}=\sum_{k=0}^{a-1}2^{b(k+1)}-\sum_{k=0}^{a-1}2^{bk}\\\underbrace{=}_{\text{change of index}} \sum_{k=1}^{a}2^{bk}-\sum_{k=0}^{a-1}2^{bk}=2^{ab}-1
